message.body: Guess what? I'm coming to boston with mom today to Move some stuff in!!!! What's your evening like? Want to do diner?
Yay! Actually the whole group is going to dinner tonight. Check with Ariel, you should join!

Actually we (mom 2) can't do dinner but I'd love to see you. We are going back to westchester tonight....this isn't official move in yet!!! But when do you get off work... You want to come to my place and hang for a hot minute?
